iah]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} '''[[Chris Wakelin]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20136 || {{flagicon|ENG}} Nico Elton\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Jamie Cope]] || align=\"center\"| 9\u2013'''10''' || {{flagicon|ENG}} '''[[Steve Davis]]'''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|NOR}} '''[[Kurt Maflin]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20135 || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[David Grace (snooker player)|David Grace]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:lightgrey\" |\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} '''[[Mark Joyce]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20136 || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Ian Burns (snooker player)|Ian Burns]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Anthony Hamilton (snooker player)|Anthony Hamilton]] || align=\"center\"| 3\u2013'''10''' || {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Zhang Anda]]'''\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Zhou Yuelong]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20138 || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Zak Surety]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Liang Wenbo]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20134 || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Chris Norbury]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:lightgrey\" |\n|-\n| {{flagicon|CHN}} '''[[Xiao Guodong]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20131 || {{flagicon|SIN}} Ong Jia Jun\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} '''[[Liam Highfield]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20131 || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Oliver Brown (snooker player)|Oliver Brown]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Kyren Wilson]] || align=\"center\"| 3\u2013'''10''' || {{nowrap|{{flagicon|THA}} '''[[Thanawat Thirapongpaiboon]]'''}}\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} '''[[Jimmy Robertson (snooker player)|Jimmy Robertson]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20137 || {{flagicon|MAS}} [[Thor Chuan Leong]]\n|-\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:lightgrey\" |\n|-\n| {{flagicon|THA}} '''[[Dechawat Poomjaeng]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20138 || {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Daniel Wells (snooker player)|Daniel Wells]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|ENG}} '''[[Robbie Williams (snooker player)|Robbie Williams]]''' || align=\"center\"| '''10'''\u20133 || {{flagicon|ENG}} [[Lee Page]]\n|-\n| {{flagicon|THA}} '